{"route":{"route":"/posts/8b98169e/","outputPath":"posts/8b98169e/index.html","kind":"post","title":"安卓使用dalvikvm运行java(termux运行java)","language":"zh-Hans","params":{"abbrlink":"8b98169e"}},"description":"一直想要使用termux来在安卓上写java,但termux上只有ecj可以使java编译为目标文件class,却不能使其编译为可执行文件 发现通过安卓自带的dalvikvm可以运行,只是步骤繁琐一些 安装所需工具 termux上安装 ecj 和 dx就可以了 编译为class文件 编译成dex文件 使用dalvikv","post":{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/安卓使用dalvikvm运行java(termux运行java).md","route":"/posts/8b98169e/","abbrlink":"8b98169e","title":"安卓使用dalvikvm运行java(termux运行java)","date":"2019-02-02 23:02:35","updated":"2019-02-02 23:02:35","tags":["android","java"],"categories":["android"],"language":"zh-Hans","htmlLang":"zh-Hans","locale":"zh_CN","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"zh-CN","excerptMarkdown":"","excerptHtml":"","bodyMarkdown":"","bodyHtml":"<p>一直想要使用termux来在安卓上写java,但termux上只有ecj可以使java编译为目标文件class,却不能使其编译为可执行文件<br>\n发现通过安卓自带的dalvikvm可以运行,只是步骤繁琐一些</p>\n<h2 id=\"安装所需工具\">安装所需工具</h2>\n<p>termux上安装 ecj 和 dx就可以了</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki code-block language-bash\"><code><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0\">apt</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> install</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> ecj</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> dx</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"编译为class文件\">编译为class文件</h2>\n<pre class=\"shiki code-block language-bash\"><code><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0\">ecj</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> XXX.java</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"编译成dex文件\">编译成dex文件</h2>\n<pre class=\"shiki code-block language-bash\"><code><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0\">dx</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> --dex</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> --output=XXX.dex</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> XXX.class</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"使用dalvikvm运行\">使用dalvikvm运行</h2>\n<pre class=\"shiki code-block language-bash\"><code><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0\">dalvikvm</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> -cp</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> XXX.dex</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> XXX</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>参考: <a href=\"https://bbs.pediy.com/thread-184592.htm\">使用 dalvikvm 执行一个运行于命令行的 Hello World</a></p>\n","rawMarkdown":"","plainText":"","toc":[{"id":"安装所需工具","text":"安装所需工具","level":2},{"id":"编译为class文件","text":"编译为class文件","level":2},{"id":"编译成dex文件","text":"编译成dex文件","level":2},{"id":"使用dalvikvm运行","text":"使用dalvikvm运行","level":2}],"slugForSearch":"8b98169e","comments":true,"math":false,"mermaid":false}}